name: Over the city
description: Over the city (Last of the series)------------------------------------ The inspiration behind the image.--------------------------------- Maybe after knowing some of this you’ll have more context to why I created this image. I had a motorcycle accident at 18 which resulted in a spinal cord injury, broken clavicle, broken ribs, and internal bleeding. I had a spinal fusion and was told that they weren’t sure if I was going to live but that I definitely would never walk again .
